{{flavour|Summons some creatures from one of the Snake Pit, the Spider Nest, the Swamp, the Shoals, the Elven Halls, the Vaults, or the Crypt; the specific branch varies with the caster.}}

'''Forceful Invitation''' is a monster-only spell which summons 1d3 monsters from one of the following randomly selected [[branch]]es, with a given branch being equally likely to be fixed per-caster. Its summon cap is 3.

